actions.text: Referred to House Committee on House Administration.

official_title: Resolution providing for the printing of additional copies of the House Report No. 94-199.

summary.text: Provides for the printing of 300 additional copies, for the use of the Committee on Armed Services of the House of Representatives, of the House report entitled "Authorizing Appropriations, Fiscal Year 1976 and the Period Beginning July 1, 1976, and ending September 30, 1976, for Military Procurement; Research and Development; Strengths for Active-Duty Military Components, Reserve Components and Civilian Personnel of the Defense Establishment; Military Training Student Loads; and for Other Purposes".

titles.title: Resolution providing for the printing of additional copies of the House Report No. 94-199.
